cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the problem of designing models for multitask learning, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG). The evaluation is performed on the GLUE benchmark for natural language understanding, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses automated curriculum learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions off-policy evaluation, which is a technique used in reinforcement learning, computer vision, and natural language processing (cs.CV, cs.NE).
